A bodysuit is a skin-tight garment that covers the body highlighting its contours. The lightweight and elasticity of the fabrics used facilitate movement. A bodysuit usually lends itself very well to sportswear.
The Slim line garments are quite tight fitting, not too tight and not too thick. These garments follow the contours of the body without constraining it which means they are comfortable.
The Regular fit line ensures a comfortable and generous fit thanks to the choice of cuts and fabrics.

Coleman 6014 Sunglasses Product Info

Coleman CC1 6014 Sunglasses take a broad approach to sport sunglasses, with wide frames, thick temples, and an attractive aesthetic. These effective Coleman sunglasses utilize sturdyimage polycarbonate frames in a wraparound design to sit comfortably and securely on your face. The frames feature a golden stripe with the Coleman logo where the temple meets the frame, and the full-frame lens border completes the look of the 6014 sunglasses. Clear vision is simple, even on intensely bright days, thanks to the polarized TAC lens on the Coleman CC-1 6014 Wraparound Shades, which feature anti-glare properties to let you enjoy a day on the beach or the ski slopes with the sunglasses. The simple style of the polarized sunglasses is ideal for either gender, and their sleek curves and ergonomic construction will make them comfortable on most face shapes. For a pair of sturdy sunglasses for your active lifestyle, wear the Coleman CC 1 6014 Polycarbonate Frame Sun Glasses.
